OL,5,C'crisis'
OL,7,FWales' Culture Minister has hit back
OL,8,Fat criticism of his performance in his
OL,9,Frole amid claims the arts sector is in
OL,10,F'crisis'.
OL,12,FJack Sargeant MS has come under fire
OL,13,Fafter a string of headlines including
OL,14,Fthe temporary closure of National
OL,15,FMuseum Cardiff, music courses at
OL,16,FCardiff University being dropped and
OL,17,Fcuts to the Welsh National Opera (WNO).
