OL,7,FThe claim of a funding 'crisis' came
OL,8,Ffrom the Arts Council of Wales, which
OL,9,Fdistributes public funding to arts
OL,10,Fgroups.
OL,12,FWhen it was put to the minister by a
OL,13,FSenedd committee, he said: "I wouldn't
OL,14,Fdescribe it as a crisis myself."
