OL,3,CCulture Minister hits back at
OL,4,Ccriticism amid claims the sector is in
OL,5,C'crisis'
OL,7,FSpeaking on ITV Wales' Sharp End
OL,8,Fprogramme on Tuesday, the culture
OL,9,Fminister said: "Where I started my
OL,10,Fjourney as a former engineering
OL,11,Fapprentice, as someone who spent time
OL,12,Fon the shop floor and is now minister,
OL,13,FI think that is a positive thing,
OL,14,Fdespite what The Times say, trying to
OL,15,Fundermine shop floor workers or
OL,16,Fapprentices in Wales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
