OL,3,CCulture Minister hits back at
OL,4,Ccriticism amid claims the sector is in
OL,5,C'crisis'
OL,7,F"We need more people with experiences
OL,8,Fthat reflect the nation in positions
OL,9,Flike mine. So I'm proud to be culture
OL,10,Fminister. I'll go on fighting for the
OL,11,Fsector every single day, making the
OL,12,Fcase for the sector, working with the
OL,13,Fsector and delivering for the sector."
OL,15,FSharp End panellist Mick Antoniw MS
OL,16,Fdefended his colleague, calling the
OL,17,Fwrite-up in The Times "a snobby and
OL,18,Fpatronising article suggesting that
OL,19,Fsomeone from an apprenticeship and
OL,20,Fworking class background can't be a
OL,21,Fminister for culture".
