OL,3,CCulture Minister hits back at
OL,4,Ccriticism amid claims the sector is in
OL,5,C'crisis'
OL,7,FA Senedd Committee report found that
OL,8,Fafter a decade of cuts, Wales ranks
OL,9,Fthird from bottom of European
OL,10,Fcountries in terms of spending per
OL,11,Fperson on recreational and sporting
OL,12,Fservices and second from bottom for
OL,13,Fcultural services.
OL,15,FMr Sargeant, who became Minister for
OL,16,FCulture, Skills and Social Partnership
OL,17,Fin September last year, added that
OL,18,Fhe's "alive to the challenges" facing
OL,19,Fthe arts and culture sectors in Wales.
