OL,3,CCulture Minister hits back at
OL,4,Ccriticism amid claims the sector is in
OL,5,C'crisis'
OL,7,FHe said: "One of the first things I
OL,8,Fdid was give an extra #1m to the
OL,9,Fsector through the resilience fund.
OL,10,FThe WNO received #755,000 for that
OL,11,Ffund.
OL,13,F"Capital investment from the Welsh
OL,14,FGovernment into this sector is up
OL,15,Fthree times more than it was a decade
OL,16,Fago.
