OL,3,CCulture Minister hits back at
OL,4,Ccriticism amid claims the sector is in
OL,5,C'crisis'
OL,7,F"The investment into Theatr Clwyd `
OL,8,F#28.5 million ` just shows how
OL,9,Fimportant this sector is to the Welsh
OL,10,FGovernment and how important it is to
OL,11,Fmyself," he continued.
OL,13,FThe Welsh Government's final budget
OL,14,Fwill be published on Thursday (20
OL,15,FFebruary) and will face a vote in the
OL,16,FSenedd on 4 March.
